This is one of the best Thai food in San Francisco. If you like duck, this is the place for you.  You must try their Pad kee mao with duck! The portion is great size and you definitely get your money’s worth.  The food is always consistently good! The service is always fast and superb! Little wait time!

Live a few blocks from here and get Jitlada often. It is the best Thai food in the city — the pad kee mao and evil princess curry are to die for. Everyone I’ve introduced to Jitlada agrees it is the best they’ve had. Staff is so kind.

The pad see ew pork was not as tasty and some noodles were still a little tough.  The papaya salad was great!  I recommend and will try it again.

Best Thai restaurant in Japantown in San Francisco! My husband and I google searched for Thai restaurant near by and found this place. The food was amazing and the owner was super nice. Definitely coming back for sure.
